data.description: Beautiful three bedroom two bath home that has been updated which includes fresh paint, wood look tile flooring in kitchen, breakfast/family room and in all bedrooms.  The kitchen features updated countertops,, microwave, dishwasher and stove.  Kitchen is open to the to the family room that has a cozy wood burning fireplace with gas starter.  Primary bathroom and secondary have updated with new bath cabinets and fixture.    All of this plus no back neighbors and a nice size back yard!  Convenient to Beltway 8, Highway 90 and Highway 59.  This property won't last long.
